  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à D-Bus GLib</title>

    <para>
      Le paquet <application>D-Bus GLib</application> contient les interfaces
<application>GLib</application> de l'API <application>D-Bus</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs111_checked;

